flowchart TD
    A1[POST /jobs/intake] --> A2[Middleware checks]
    A2 --> A3{Session valid}
    A3 -->|no| A4[401]
    A3 -->|yes| A5[Normalize URL + parse job id]
    A5 --> A6{Duplicate exists}
    A6 -->|yes| A7[duplicate decision required]
    A6 -->|no| A8[Create job status=draft]

    A8 --> B1[POST /jobs/{id}/extract]
    B1 --> B2{QUEUE_DRIVER}
    B2 -->|inline| B3[Inline extraction]
    B2 -->|dramatiq| B4[Enqueue to Redis broker]
    B4 --> B5[Worker consume task]
    B5 --> B6[Acquire Redis lock]
    B6 --> B7{Lock acquired}
    B7 -->|no| B8[Skip duplicate task]
    B7 -->|yes| B9[Firecrawl scrape]
    B3 --> B9

    B9 --> B10{Scrape success}
    B10 -->|yes| B11[Persist markdown + status=ready]
    B10 -->|no| B12[Persist error + requires_manual_markdown]
    B12 --> B13[POST /jobs/{id}/manual-markdown]
    B13 --> B14[Persist manual markdown + status=ready]

    B11 --> C1[GET/PATCH outputs]
    B14 --> C1
    C1 --> C2[History/status/submission APIs]
    C2 --> C3[Metrics + audit + logs]
